pageContext.claim: “A very big Caravan of over 20,000 people started up through Mexico. It has been reduced in size by Mexico but is still coming. Mexico must apprehend the remainder or we will be forced to close that section of the Border & call up the Military. The Coyotes & Cartels have weapons!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump doubled the size of most estimates of the caravan. It's about 10,000 people, according to news reports.
